                    <a class="icon_commend" href="http://giaitri.vnexpress.net/tin-tuc/gioi-sao/trong-nuoc/nguyen-quang-than-da-ngan-yeu-den-dien-cuong-1881927.html#box_comment" style="white-space: nowrap; display: none;"><span class="txt_num_comment font_icon" data-type="comment" data-objecttype="1" data-objectid="1881927"></span></a>                </li>
